,294||[[Garry Hay|Hay]] 90'\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|R4 Replay||6 March 2001||[[Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|Inverness Caledonian Thistle]]||H||2\u20131||6,528||[[Kevin McGowne|McGowne]] 60', [[Paul Wright (footballer)|Wright]] 90'\n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|QF||10 March 2001||[[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]]||H||0\u20131||8,287||\n|}\n\n===Scottish League Cup===\n{{Main article|2000\u201301 Scottish League Cup}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:center\"\n!Match!!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|R2||22 August 2000||[[Clyde F.C.|Clyde]]||A||2\u20131||2,010||[[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Dindeleux|Dindeleux]] 112', [[Ally McCoist|McCoist]] 113'\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|R3||5 September 2000||[[St Johnstone F.C.|St Johnstone]]||A||1\u20130||3,231||[[Ally McCoist|McCoist]] 68'\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|QF||31 October 2000||[[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]]||H||2\u20131||7,819||[[Andy McLaren|McLaren]] 46', [[Craig Dargo|Dargo]] 71'\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|SF||6 February 2001||[[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]]||N||3\u20130||9,213||[[Andy McLaren|McLaren]] 39', [[Craig Dargo|Dargo]] 69', [[Peter Canero|Canero]] 78'\n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|Final||18 March 2001||[[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]]||N||0\u20133||48,883||\n|}\n\n==Final league table==\n{{:2000\u201301 Scottish Premier League|showteam=KIL}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.soccerbase.com/teams/team.sd?team_id=2472&season_id=128&teamTabs=results Kilmarnock 2000\u201301] at Soccerbase.com (select relevant season from dropdown list)\n\n{{2000\u201301 in Scottish football}}\n{{Kilmarnock F.C.}}\n{{Kilmarnock F.C. seasons}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2000-01 Kilmarnock F.C. season}}\n[[Category:Kilmarnock F.C. seasons]]\n[[Category:Scottish football clubs 2000\u201301 season|Kilmarnock]]\n", "name_user": "Aidan Lynn 1998", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wiki